Clean up the recap below for {{ context.game_title }}. Keep it specific and
actionable — do NOT flatten it into vague "keep exploring" advice. Make three
kinds of edits and nothing else:

1. Remove spoilers:
   - Boss names and the existence/location of bosses the player hasn't met.
   - Plot twists, story outcomes, character fates.
   - Locations of major story items the player has NOT already mentioned.
   (KEEP area names, directions, routes, objectives, abilities, and anything the
   player already mentioned — those are not spoilers.)

2. Remove any meta references: never mention guides, walkthroughs, wikis,
   websites, checklists, IGN, "the source", or that any search was done. Talk
   only about the in-game world.

3. Strip ALL Markdown: no asterisks, no bold, no headings, no numbered sections.
   Keep the plain-text shape:

   Previously on {{ context.game_title }}: <recap>

   What you could do this session:
   - <step>
   - <step>

